0aim%20of%20coming%20up%20with%20an%20action%20plan%20for%20the%20next%20Lok%20Sabha%20Polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20meeting%20of%20the%20joint%20opposition%20was%20held%20in%20Patna%20on%20June%2023%20and%20the%20second%20meeting%20was%20held%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20July%2017%20and%20July%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693592820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F7e5d5698_arvind-kejriwal-pti_625x300_01_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal-on-reports-of-infighting-in-india-alliance-no-conflict-4349670%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20Friday%20asserted%20that%20there%20is%20no%20conflict%20among%20the%20parties%20of%20the%20Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%20alliance.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal-on-reports-of-infighting-in-india-alliance-no-conflict-4349670%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal-on-reports-of-infighting-in-india-alliance-no-conflict-4349670%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-chief-minister-arvind-kejriwal-on-reports-of-infighting-in-india-alliance-no-conflict-4349670%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jet%20Airways%20Founder%20Arrested%20In%20Rs%20538%20Crore%20Alleged%20Bank%20Fraud%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJet%20Airways%20founder%20Naresh%20Goyal%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20an%20alleged%20Rs%20538%20crore%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20Canara%20Bank%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%20was%20taken%20into%20custody%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%2C%20following%20a%20long%20session%20of%20questioning%20at%20the%20ED's%20office%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Goyal%2C%2074%2C%20will%20be%20produced%20before%20a%20special%20PMLA%20court%20in%20Mumbai%20on%20Saturday%2C%20where%20the%20ED%20will%20seek%20his%20custodial%20remand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20money%20laundering%20case%20stems%20from%20a%20first%20information%20report%20(FIR)%20of%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20against%20Jet%20Airways%2C%20Mr%20Goyal%2C%20his%20wife%20Anita%20and%20some%20former%20company%20executives%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20Rs%20538%20crore%20fraud%20case%20at%20Canara%20Bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20was%20filed%20on%20the%20bank's%20complaint%20that%20alleged%20it%20sanctioned%20credit%20limits%20and%20loans%20to%20Jet%20Airways%20(India)%20Ltd%20(JIL)%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20Rs%20848.86%20crore%2C%20of%20which%20Rs%20538.62%20crore%20is%20outstanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20had%20said%20the%20account%20was%20declared%20%26quot%3Bfraud%26quot%3B%20in%20July%202021.%20The%20bank%20alleged%20the%20forensic%20audit%20of%20JIL%20showed%20it%20paid%20%26quot%3Brelated%20companies%26quot%3B%20Rs%201%2C410.41%20crore%20out%20of%20a%20total%20commission%20expenses%2C%20thus%20siphoning%20off%20funds%20from%20JIL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FIR%20said%20personal%20expenses%20such%20as%20salaries%20of%20staff%2C%20phone%20bills%20and%20vehicle%20expenses%2C%20among%20others%2C%20of%20the%20Goyal%20family%20were%20paid%20by%20JIL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20surfaced%20during%20the%20forensic%20audit%20that%20funds%20were%20also%20siphoned%20off%20through%20Jet%20Lite%20(India)%20Ltd%20(JLL)%20by%20making%20advance%20and%20investing%20and%20subsequently%20writing%20off%20the%20same%20by%20making%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJIL%20allegedly%20diverted%20the%20funds%20for%20the%20subsidiary%20JLL%20in%20the%20form%20of%20loans%20and%20advances%20and%20investments%20extended.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693592640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-03%2F2fkb79j_naresh-goyal-afp_650x400_25_March_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjet-airways-founder-naresh-goyal-arrested-by-probe-agency-in-alleged-bank-fraud-case-4350148%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jet%20Airways%20founder%20Naresh%20Goyal%20has%20been%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20in%20an%20alleged%20Rs%20538%20crore%20money%20laundering%20case%20linked%20to%20Canara%20Bank%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjet-airways-founder-naresh-goyal-arrested-by-probe-agency-in-alleged-bank-fraud-case-4350148%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjet-airways-founder-naresh-goyal-arrested-by-probe-agency-in-alleged-bank-fraud-case-4350148%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fjet-airways-founder-naresh-goyal-arrested-by-probe-agency-in-alleged-bank-fraud-case-4350148%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lavrov%20Says%20G20%20General%20Declaration%20Will%20Be%20Blocked%20If%20Moscow%E2%80%99s%20Views%20on%20Ukraine%20Are%20Ignored%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F03152630%2FFqMbzwUWAAAmT01.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20a%20week%20left%20for%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20Russian%20foreign%20minister%20Sergei%20Lavrov%20said%20on%20Friday%20(September%201)%20that%20Moscow%20will%20block%20the%20summit%E2%80%99s%20final%20declaration%20unless%20its%20position%20on%20Ukraine%20and%20other%20issues%20were%20reflected%20in%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20skipping%20the%20event%2C%20Lavrov%20is%20due%20to%20represent%20Russia%20at%20the%20summit%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Sep%209%20and%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20will%20be%20no%20general%20declaration%20on%20behalf%20of%20all%20members%20if%20our%20position%20is%20not%20reflected%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lavrov%20told%20students%20at%20the%20Moscow%20State%20Institute%20of%20International%20Relations%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fworld%2Frussia-block-g20-declaration-if-its-views-are-ignored-lavrov-2023-09-01%2F%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Reuters%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20if%20consensus%20could%20not%20be%20reached%20at%20the%20G20%20meeting%2C%20a%20non-binding%20communique%20could%20be%20issued%20by%20the%20G20%20presidency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnother%20option%20is%20to%20adopt%20a%20document%20that%20focuses%20on%20specific%20decisions%20in%20the%20sphere%20of%20G20%20competences%2C%20and%20let%20everyone%20say%20the%20rest%20on%20their%20own%20behalf%2C%E2%80%9D%20Lavrov%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20and%20China%20agreed%20to%20two%20paragraphs%20regarding%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%20in%20the%20Bali%20G20%20declaration%20but%20withdrew%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20G20%20meetings%20chaired%20under%20India%E2%80%99s%20presidency%20have%20had%20%E2%80%9Cchair%E2%80%99s%20summary%20and%20outcome%20documents%E2%80%9D%20in%20lieu%20of%20joint%20statements%2C%20so%20as%20to%20circumvent%20the%20lack%20of%20consensus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Lavrov%2C%20Russian%20ambassador%20to%20India%20Denis%20Alipov%20also%20reiterated%20that%20there%20was%20no%20consensus%20on%20the%20text%20related%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20underlined%20that%20Russia%20hoped%20the%20summit%20will%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9Chuge%20success%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CObviously%2C%20the%20situation%20is%20complicated.%20There%20is%20no%20consensus%20on%20%5Bthe%20Ukraine%20issue%5D%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alipov%20said%20at%20an%20interactive%20session%20in%20the%20Delhi-based%20Foreign%20Correspondents%E2%80%99%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20no%20consensus%20on%20only%20one%20issue%20and%20there%20is%20consensus%20on%20all%20other%20issues%2C%20what%20shall%20we%20do%20in%20this%20situation%3F%E2%80%9D%20Alipov%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20should%20remove%20the%20non-consensual%20issue%20from%20the%20agenda%20to%20agree%20on%20other%20very%20topical%20issues%20such%20as%20climate%20change%2C%20sustainable%20development%2C%20financial%20crisis%20%5Band%5D%20food%20crisis%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlipov%20suggested%20that%20there%20are%20bodies%20like%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council%20which%20should%20deliberate%20on%20the%20Ukraine%20conflict%2C%20and%20that%20Russia%20is%20open%20for%20discussions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20G20%20was%20established%20for%20resolving%20financial%20and%20economic%20problems%20that%20the%20world%20faces%2C%20and%20not%20to%20deliberate%20on%20geopolitical%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20no%20consensus%2C%20then%20political%20issues%20should%20not%20be%20discussed%2C%E2%80%9D%20Alipov%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693592363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F03152630%2FFqMbzwUWAAAmT01.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Flavrov-says-g20-general-declaration-will-be-blocked-if-moscows-views-on-ukraine-are-ignored%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Lavrov%2C%20Russian%20ambassador%20to%20India%20Denis%20Alipov%20also%20reiterated%20that%20there%20was%20no%20consensus%20on%20the%20text%20related%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.