0per%20their%20own%20style%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bench%20of%20justices%20Suresh%20Kumar%20Kait%20and%20Neena%20Bansal%20Krishna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%20by%20the%20woman's%20partner%20who%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bmissing%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20allegedly%20taken%20away%20by%20her%20family%20members%20as%20they%20were%20against%20their%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20last%20date%20of%20hearing%2C%20the%20woman%20was%20produced%20before%20the%20court%20which%20had%20then%20directed%20the%20police%20to%20take%20her%20to%20a%20shelter%20home%20and%20make%20necessary%20arrangements%20for%20her%20boarding%20and%20lodging%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20August%2029%2C%20the%20bench%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20find%20that%20the%20woman%20is%2022%20years%20old%20and%20as%20per%20law%2C%20she%20cannot%20be%20forced%20to%20go%20to%20any%20place%20against%20her%20wishes%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20of%20the%20considered%20opinion%20that%20the%20woman%20is%20at%20liberty%20to%20stay%20with%20whomsoever%20and%20wherever%20she%20wants%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20woman's%20father%2C%20who%20was%20also%20present%20in%20the%20court%2C%20assured%20the%20bench%20that%20all%20her%20documents%20and%20belongings%20would%20be%20handed%20over%20to%20her%20through%20a%20police%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20also%20permitted%20the%20couple%20to%20live%20together%20at%20a%20place%20where%20the%20petitioner%20was%20staying%20and%20directed%20the%20Station%20House%20Officer%20(SHO)%20of%20the%20police%20station%20concerned%20to%20share%20the%20contact%20number%20of%20the%20woman%20sub-inspector%20and%20beat%20constable%20with%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20high%20court%20had%20earlier%20directed%20the%20parents%20and%20maternal%20uncle%20of%20the%20woman%20to%20undergo%20counselling%20in%20order%20to%20prepare%20themselves%20t