2%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-airlift-planes-targeted-attack-launched-from-inside-russia-territory-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22More%20than%20150%20migrants%20in%20small%20boats%20rescued%20off%20Greece's%20Aegean%20Sea%20islands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693587653000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-103292806%2Cimgsize-96986.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmore-than-150-migrants-in-small-boats-rescued-off-greeces-aegean-sea-islands%2Farticleshow%2F103292768.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F103292768.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EGreek%20authorities%20on%20Friday%20rescued%20more%20than%20150%20people%2C%20including%20several%20children%2C%20who%20were%20heading%20in%20small%20boats%20from%20Turkey%20to%20the%20nearby%20eastern%20Aegean%20Sea%20islands%2C%20the%20coast%20guard%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmore-than-150-migrants-in-small-boats-rescued-off-greeces-aegean-sea-islands%2Farticleshow%2F103292768.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmore-than-150-migrants-in-small-boats-rescued-off-greeces-aegean-sea-islands%2Famp_articleshow%2F103292768.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fmore-than-150-migrants-in-small-boats-rescued-off-greeces-aegean-sea-islands%2Famp_articleshow%2F103292768.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uddhav%20Thackeray%20Explains%20Why%20A%20Convenor%20%26quot%3BNot%20Needed%26quot%3B%20For%20INDIA%20Bloc%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20on%20Friday%20said%20there%20was%20no%20need%20for%20a%20convenor%20of%20the%20opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%20as%20it%20has%20coordination%20committees%20that%20would%20work%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20consensus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20bloc%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20former%20Maharashtra%20chief%20minister%20also%20said%20the%20logo%20of%20INDIA%20was%20put%20on%20hold%20so%20that%20people's%20suggestions%20could%20be%20sought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20suggestion%20that%20we%20take%20people's%20views%20on%20the%20logo%20since%20this%20fight%20is%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20people.%20We%20will%20seek%20their%20suggestions%20within%20a%20given%20timeframe%20and%20can%20come%20up%20with%20a%20better%20logo%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20confusion%20about%20the%20logo.%20We%20had%20two-three%20logos%20ready%20but%20put%20the%20unveiling%20on%20hold%20because%20everyone%20liked%20the%20suggestion%20that%20we%20go%20to%20the%20people.%20People's%20participation%20will%20be%20with%20us%20from%20day%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20post%20of%20convenor%20for%20the%20bloc%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20said%20there%20will%20be%20a%20coordination%20committee%20in%20each%20state%2C%20which%20%26quot%3Bwill%20be%20the%20easy%20way%20forward%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsserting%20that%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20has%20taken%20a%20step%20forward%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20decided%20to%20ensure%20one-on-one%20fight%20(against%20the%20ruling%20BJP-led%20NDA)%20wherever%20possible.%26quot%3B%20In%20Maharashtra%2C%20the%20Peasants%20and%20Workers%20Party%20(PWP)%20has%20joined%20the%20bloc%20and%20talks%20are%20underway%20with%20the%20Prakash%20Ambedkar-led%20Vanchit%20Bahujan%20Aghadi%2C%20while%20coordination%20committees%20in%20other%20states%20will%20discuss%20likewise%20(to%20bring%20more%20parties%20into%20the%20fold)%2C%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20chief%20informed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20committees%20will%20report%20to%20the%20president%20of%20the%20respective%20alliance%20partners%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20speaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20interacting%20with%20functionaries%20of%20the%20labour%20union%2C%20which%20is%20affiliated%20to%20his%20party%2C%20of%20the%20suburban%20hotel%20that%20hosted%20the%20INDIA%20meet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Thackeray%20said%20the%20two-day%20deliberations%20of%20a%20wide%20array%20of%20opposition%20parties%20was%20a%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20date%20for%20the%20next%20meeting%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20not%20announced%20at%20the%20end%20of%20these%20deliberations%20since%20it%20was%20not%20needed%20as%20all%20the%20leaders%20would%20directly%20go%20to%20the%20people%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20joint%20public%20rally%20might%20be%20held%20soon%2C%20while%20gatherings%20will%20be%20held%20in%20every%20state%2C%20Mr%20Thackeray%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%20holding%20a%20special%20session%20of%20Parliament%20during%20Ganpati%20festivities%20was%20wrong%2C%20and%20asked%20if%20this%20government%20(at%20the%20Centre)%20was%20%26quot%3Banti-Hindu%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLord%20Ganesh%20is%20called%20vighnaharta%20(remover%20of%20obstacles).%20We%20hope%20with%20his%20arrival%20the%20nation's%20troubles%20will%20end%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20an%20apparent%20swipe%20at%20the%20ruling%20dispensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20Minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%20announced%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20convened%20a%20special%20five-day%20session%20of%20the%20Parliament%20from%20September%2018%20to%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20st