ce%201787%2C%20according%20to%20Bank%20of%20America.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20decline%20comes%20after%20US%20Treasury%20bonds%20suffered%20their%20worst%20annual%20loss%20since%201788.%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20Chart%20of%20the%20Day%20is%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fbac-stock%5C%22%3EBank%20of%20America%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20shows%20that%20US%20Treasury%20bonds%20are%20headed%20for%20their%20longest%20stretch%20of%20losses%20ever%2C%20dating%20all%20the%20way%20back%20to%201787.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%2010-year%20Treasury%20is%20on%20track%20to%20see%20its%20third%20consecutive%20annual%20loss.%20The%2010-year%20bond%20fell%203.9%25%20in%202021%2C%20and%20tumbled%2017%25%20in%202022%2C%20which%20was%20its%20worst%20annual%20loss%20since%201788.%20So%20far%20this%20year%2C%20it's%20down%200.3%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B10-year%20Treasury%20on%20course%20for%20third%20consecutive%20loss...%20has%20never%20occurred%20in%20250-year%20history%20of%20US%20republic.%20Reflects%20staggering%2040%25%20jump%20in%20US%20nominal%20GDP%20(growth%20%2B%20inflation)%20since%202020%20COVID%20lows%2C%26quot%3B%20BofA%20investment%20strategist%20Michael%20Hartnett%20said%20in%20a%20Friday%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pain%20in%20bonds%20has%20been%20driven%20by%20aggressive%20interest%20rate%20hikes%20from%20the%20Federal%20Reserve.%20Since%20March%202022%2C%20the%20Fed%20has%20hiked%20interest%20rates%2011%20times%2C%20bringing%20the%20effective%20fed%20funds%20rate%20from%20nearly%200%25%20to%20more%20than%205%25%20today.%20As%20interest%20rates%20rise%2C%20bond%20prices%20fall%2C%20which%20is%20why%20bonds%20have%20performed%20so%20poorly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20long%20stretch%20of%20pain%20in%20fixed%20income%2C%20investors%20poured%20%241.7%20billion%20into%20bonds%20this%20week%2C%20representing%20the%2023rd%20straight%20week%20of%20inflows%2C%20according%20to%20BofA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchart-of-the-day-us-treasurys-1787-longest-stretch-losses-2023-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693583827000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f208f25114270019af4d87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fchart-of-the-day-us-treasurys-1787-longest-stretch-losses-2023-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3B10-year%20Treasury%20on%20course%20for%20third%20consecutive%20loss...%20has%20never%20occurred%20in%20250-year%20history%20of%20US%20republic%2C%26quot%3B%20Bank%20of%20America%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fbonds%2Fchart-of-the-day-us-treasurys-1787-longest-stretch-losses-2023-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mississippi%20Hunter%20Kills%20Longest%20Alligator%20Weighing%20364%20Kg%2C%20Pics%20Go%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMississippi%20hunters%20have%20killed%20the%20longest%20alligator%20ever%20found%20in%20the%20US%20State.%20According%20to%20the%20Mississippi%20Department%20of%20Wildfire%2C%20Fisheries%20and%20Parks%20(MDWFP)%2C%20the%20record-breaking%20animal%20measured%2014%20feet%20and%203%20inches%20long%20and%20weighed%20364kg.%20The%20alligator%20was%20captured%20in%20the%20state's%20Yazoo%20River.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.usatoday.com%2Fstory%2Fnews%2Fnation%2F2023%2F08%2F28%2Fmassive-alligator-captured-mississippi-breaks-record%2F70697288007%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EUSA%20Today%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20fight%20to%20catch%20the%20alligator%20lasted%20from%209%20p.m.%20to%204%20a.m.%20Hunter%20Donald%20Woods%20told%20the%20media%20outlet%20that%20the%