ants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20July%2C%20Subway%20said%2010%2C000%20stores%20have%20been%20remodeled%20in%20North%20America%2C%20%26quot%3Bwith%20more%20to%20come.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EStores%20are%20cannibalizing%20each%20other.%20Keep%20cutting%20store%20counts.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221029%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subway%20Google%20map%20of%20stores%20in%20Orange%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0c40857bff7001947a486%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22848%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESo%20many%20Subways.%20%3Cp%3EGoogle%20Maps%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESubway%20grew%20too%20fast%20under%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubway-founder-ceo-fred-deluca-inside-story-2021-6%3Fr%3Dsubway-lp%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFred%20DeLuca%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20franchisees%20continue%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20for%20the%20greedy%20growth%20trajectory.%20The%20Miami-based%20chain%20closed%20more%20than%206%2C500%20restaurants%20between%202015%20and%202022%2C%20and%20its%20US%20store%20count%20stood%20at%2020%2C576%20at%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20the%20market-research%20firm%20Technomic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20need%20to%20trim%20more%20fat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20where%20I%20live%20in%20Southern%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%2020%20Subway%20restaurants%20less%20than%20three%20miles%20from%20where%20I%20live%20in%20Orange%2C%20California.%20Of%20those%2C%2050%25%20have%20another%20store%200.1%20miles%20or%20less%20from%20another%20Subway.%20There's%20not%20enough%20interest%20in%20Subway%20to%20sustain%20these%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20visited%20four%20of%20these%20stores%20at%20lunch%20and%20dinner.%20Each%20time%2C%20there%20were%20three%20or%20fewer%20people%20ordering%20food.%20In%20most%20cases%2C%20I%20was%20the%20only%20person%20ordering%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20analytics%20firm%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FPlacer.ai%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPlacer.ai%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20foot%20traffic%20at%20Subway%20has%20inched%20up%20this%20year.%C2%A0In%20July%2C%20visits%20were%20up%200.4%25%20year%20over%20year%2C%20but%20traffic%20was%20still%20down%2018.5%25%20compared%20to%20July%202019.%20In%20May%2C%20traffic%20was%20down%2021.6%25%20compared%20to%20four%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EFix%20the%20bread%20and%20the%20tuna%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221507%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subway's%20six%20inch%20tuna%20sandwich%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0c5f157bff7001947a8b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221283%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThere%20was%20barely%20any%20tuna%20in%20this%20sandwich%2C%20served%20on%20stale-tasting%20bread.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20Subway%20rolled%20out%20artisanal%20loaves%20of%20bread%2C%20upgraded%20soups%2C%20and%20added%20new%20meats%20and%20dressings.%20It%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.subway.com%2F2021-07-06-Subway-Debuts-Largest-Menu-Update-in-Brands-History%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebilled%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20most%20extensive%20menu%20update%20in%20the%20brand's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20they%20didn't%20upgrade%20was%20the%20tuna%2C%20which%20has%20been%20the%20subject%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsubway-tuna-is-a-mixture-of-various-concoctions-lawsuit-claims-2021-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtroversy%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years.%20In%20lawsuits%20and%20media%20publications%2C%20Subway%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20mislabeling%20its%20tuna%20because%20the%20product%20sold%20in%20stores%20does%20not%20contain%20actual%20tuna%20fish.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%202021%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20conducted%20its%20lab%20test%20and%20published%20a%20report%20stating%20that%20it%20found%20no%20tuna%20DNA%20in%20Subway%20tuna%20sandwiches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubway%20has%20called%20these%20accusations%20meritless.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20are%20so%20confident%20in%20their%20tuna%20that%20it%20was%20the%20one%20item%20they%20didn't%20upgrade%20during%20the%20big%202021%20menu%20overhaul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20many%20of%20Subway's%20core%20protein%20choices%20were%20improved%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Eat%20Fresh%20Refresh%2C%20one%20ingredient%20that%20doesn't%20need%20an%20upgrade%20is%20the%20Subway%20high-quality%2C%20premium%20tuna%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnewsroom.subway.com%2F2021-07-06-Subway-Debuts-Largest-Menu-Update-in-Brands-History%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estated%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021.%20%26quot%3BSubway%20sources%20tuna%20from%20leading%20global%20food%20suppliers%20that%20have%20a%20reputation%20for%20working%20diligently%20with%20food%20safety%20and%20quality%20experts%20to%20ensure%20consistent%2C%20high-quality%20products%20at%20every%20stage%20of%20the%20supply%20chain.%20The%20100%25%20wild-caught%20tuna%20remains%20a%20fan%20favorite%20among%20sub%20lovers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20the%20tuna%20sandwich%20at%20a%20Subway%20in%20Santa%20Ana%2C%20California%2C%20an%20aging%20stand-alone%20store%20in%20a%20former%20adobe-style%20Taco%20Bell%20building.%20The%206-inch%20sandwich%2C%20served%20on%20white%20artisanal%20Italian%20bread%2C%20came%20with%20two%20scoops%20of%20tuna%20that%20looked%20more%20like%20tuna%20spread.%20The%20sandwich%20artist%20put%20only%20two%20tiny%20scoops%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20bread%20loaf.%20The%20ingredients%20I%20added%20%E2%80%94%20onions%2C%20lettuce%2C%20and%20pickles%20%E2%80%94overpowered%20the%20tuna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20tasted%20like%20tuna%2C%20but%20I%20would%20not%20call%20this%20a%20premium%20product.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20let's%20talk%20about%20the%20bread.%20There's%20nothing%20artisanal%20about%20these%20newly%20formulated%20loaves.%20During%20my%20four%20visits%2C%20I%20tried%20the%20artisanal%20Italian%2C%20the%20hearty%20multigrain%2C%20and%20the%20Italian%20herb-and%20cheese%20bread.%20Subway%20said%20it%20tapped%20%26quot%3Ba%20panel%20of%20world-class%20bakers%20over%20two%20years%20to%20develop%26quot%3B%20these%20new%20recipes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20needs%20to%20tap%20a%20few%20more%20bakers%2C%20because%20the%20bread%20is%20terrible.%20Each%20store%20served%20bread%20that%20was%20stale%20and%20flavorless.%20Even%20the%20herb-and-cheese%20bread%20had%20no%20flavor%20to%20it.%20A%20stale%20French%20baguette%20tastes%20better%20than%20these%20loaves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EKeep%20your%20stores%20clean%20and%20stocked%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Subway%20Cafe%20story%20with%20dirty%20tables%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64f0c66e5114270019ae66f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20Subway%20Cafe%20store%20in%20Orange%2C%20California%2C%20had%20tables%20topped%20with%20bread%20crumbs%2C%20dirty%20napkins%2C%20and%20trash%20on%20the%20floor.%20%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20four%20stores%20I%20visited%20had%20dirty%20floors%20and%20tables.%20Usually%2C%20I%20give%20a%20restaurant%20a%20pass%20on%20this%20if%20there%20are%20lines%20out%20the%20door%20and%20there's%20no%20staff%20available%20for%20busing%20and%20cleaning%20tables.%20But%20most%20of%20the%20stores%20I%20went%20to%20were%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20unkempt%20restaurants%20looked%20especially%20terrible%20in%20the%20remodeled%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Subway%20Cafe%20near%20Chapman%20University%20in%20Orange%20was%20filthy.%20At%20least%20three%20employees%20were%20working%2C%20and%20I%20was%20the%20only%20customer%20in%20the%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubway%20and%20its%