een%20Rajamaran.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FGramiya-2-1693575219.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FGramiya-2-1693575219-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FGramiya-2-1693575219-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FGramiya-2-1693575219-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2FGramiya-2-1693575219-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-328870%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESibi%20started%20Gramiya%20with%20college%20friends%20Mohammad%20Yaseen%20(right)%20and%20Naveen%20Rajamaran.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThereafter%2C%20oil%20is%20extracted%20from%20these%20seeds%20on%20a%20stone%20mill%20with%20a%20wooden%20pestle.%20Usually%2C%20during%20the%20processing%2C%20hydrogenation%20method%20is%20used%20to%20maximise%20the%20amount%20of%20oil%20extracted%20from%20the%20seed.%20In%20this%20method%2C%20oils%20are%20processed%20in%20traditional%20steel%20grinders%20using%20steam%20boilers%20where%20heating%20temperatures%20are%20as%20high%20as%20180%20degrees%20Celsius.%20This%20oil%20breaks%20into%20high%20trans%20fat%20content%2C%20which%20increases%20cardiovascular%20risks%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%202022%20study%20by%20the%20%3Cem%3EInternational%20Journal%20of%20Food%20and%20Nutritional%20Sciences%3C%2Fem%3E%20reveals%20that%20because%20of%20this%20procedure%2C%20the%20seeds%20are%20stripped%20of%20all%20naturally%20occurring%20nutrients%20and%20antioxidants%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20final%20product%20that%20is%20devoid%20of%20flavour%20and%20offers%20no%20positive%20effects%20on%20our%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20just%20crush%20seeds%20hard%20enough%20to