e%20critical%20in%20getting%20policymakers%20to%20hear%20and%20incorporate%20the%20knowledge%2C%20views%20and%20concerns%20of%20those%20who%20advocate%20climate%20justice%20and%20sustainable%20livelihoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParticipants%20of%20the%20event%20have%20pledged%20to%20come%20together%20to%20work%20across%20borders%20on%20these%20issues%2C%20with%20the%20Southasia%20Peace%20Action%20Network%20providing%20them%20a%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EMalinda%20Seneviratne%20is%20former%20Editor-in-Chief%20of%20The%20Nation%2C%20Colombo%2C%20and%20now%20contributes%20regular%20columns%20to%20the%20Daily%20Mirror%20and%20Daily%20News%2C%20Sri%20Lanka.%20He%20is%20also%20a%20published%20poet%20who%20has%20been%20awarded%20the%20Gratiaen%20Prize%20for%20his%20poetry%20collection%20%E2%80%98Edges%E2%80%99%20and%20a%20two-time%20winner%20of%20the%20H.%20A.%20I.%20Goonetilleka%20Prize%20for%20the%20best%20literary%20translation%20awarded%20by%20the%20Gratiaen%20Trust%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ci%3E.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20is%20a%20%3C%2Fi%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fsapannews.com%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ESapan%20News%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%20syndicated%20feature.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693571836000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01173239%2Fimage-1270.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsouth-asian-youth-raise-a-collective-voice-for-climate-justice-and-sustainable-livelihoods%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Climate%20activists%20from%20various%20South%20Asian%20nations%20discuss%20the%20importance%20of%20giving%20voice%20to%20conscience%20and%20protecting%20biodiversity%2C%20and%20holding%20those%20responsible%20for%20environmental%20intrusions%20accountable.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fsouth-asian-youth-raise-a-collective-voice-for-climate-justice-and-sustainable-li