sion%20of%20the%20fastener%20in%201890%2C%20receiving%20a%20patent%20for%20his%20%E2%80%9Cclasp%20locker%E2%80%9D%20on%20August%2029%2C%201893.%20Shortly%20after%2C%20he%20presented%20his%20invention%20at%20the%20Chicago%20World%E2%80%99s%20Fair.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJudson%E2%80%99s%20clasp%20locker%20was%20designed%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20long%20shoelaces%20on%20boots.%20But%20apparently%2C%20not%20everyone%20found%C2%A0tying%20shoes%20tedious%2C%20and%20his%20invention%20was%20met%20with%20widespread%20indifference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUS%20Army%20becomes%20main%20client%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20another%20decade%20for%20Judson%20and%20his%20partners%20to%20relaunch%20the%20device%20after%20improving%20its%20technology.%20Other%20engineers%20continued%20to%20optimise%20the%20invention%2C%20including%20in%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20serial%20production%20of%20the%20mechanism%20started%2C%20the%20US%20military%20became%20one%20of%20its%20first%20bulk%20buyers%2C%20integrating%20zippers%20into%20the%20troops%E2%80%99%20clothing%20and%C2%A0gear%20during%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fworld-war-i%2Ft-17449701%5C%22%3EWorld%20War%20I%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20until%20the%20late%201930s%20that%20the%20invention%20finally%20revolutionized%20fashion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20was%20often%20the%20case%20for%20fashion%20innovations%20at%20the%20time%2C%20the%20zipper%20was%20initially%20used%20only%20for%20men%E2%80%99s%20clothing%2C%20as%20it%20was%20deemed%20inappropriate%20for%20women%20to%20wear%20clothes%20that%20could%20be%20taken%20off%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20finally%20applied%20to%20women%E2%80%99s%20clothes%2C%20zippers%20were%20placed%20discretely%20on%20the%20side%20instead%20of%20in%20the%20crotch%20area%20to%20avoid%20drawing%20attention%20to%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20intimate%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Germany%2C%20mostly%20men%20wore%20fly%20trousers%20until%C2%A0the%20late%201960s%20when%20jeans%20became%20accepted%20as%20a%20genderless%20clothing%20item.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20this%20day%2C%20many%20manufacturers%20still%20design%20pants%20differently%20according%20to%20gender%3A%20Zippers%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20fashion%20are%20traditionally%20zipped%20up%20with%20the%20left%20hand%3B%20for%20men%E2%80%99s%20clothes%2C%20with%20the%20right%20hand.%C2%A0It%E2%80%99s%20a%20legacy%20of%20the%20pre-zipper%20era%20when%20button%20plackets%20in%20women%E2%80%99s%20fashion%20were%20designed%20for%20wealthy%20ladies%20dressed%20by%20their%20maids.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20this%20distinction%20hardly%20exists%20with%20unisex%20clothing%2C%20even%20though%20it%20is%20still%20the%20norm%20for%20shirts%2C%20blouses%20and%20suits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EZippers%20on%20the%20moon%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%20made%20of%20metal%2C%20zippers%20were%20later%20made%20of%20other%20materials%2C%20such%20as%20nylon%20and%20plastic.%20Manufacturers%20have%20also%20developed%20zippers%20that%20can%20open%20from%20both%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20beyond%20the%20technological%20improvements%2C%20the%20basic%20principle%20has%20remained%20the%20same%3A%20The%20zipper%20is%20made%20of%20two%20flexible%20strips%20of%20fabric%20with%20rows%20of%20metal%20or%C2%A0plastic%20teeth%20that%20fasten%20by%20hooking%20into%20each%20other%20when%20pushed%20together%20by%20a%20slider.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%201950s%2C%20US%20space%20agency%20NASA%20also%20contributed%20to%20zipper%20technology%20when%20developing%20its%20high-pressure%20space%20suits%2C%20designing%20an%20air-tight%20sealed%20zip%20that%20could%20withstand%20pressure.%20They%C2%A0were%20used%20during%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhuman-spaceflight%2Ft-64949754%5C%22%3EApollo%2011%20mission%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%201969%2C%C2%A0the%20first%20moon%20landing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20suits%20were%20not%20suitable%C2%A0for%20longer%20ventures%20into%20space%2C%20as%20are%20common%20nowadays%2C%20which%20is%20why%20NASA%20discarded%20the%20zipper.%20Yet%20fire-resistant%20and%20chemical-resistant%20successors%20to%20the%20NASA%20technology%20are%20still%20in%20demand%20today%2C%20notably%20in%20gear%20for%20fire%20departments%20and%C2%A0chemical%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERebellion%20and%20pop%20art%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20zipper%20has%20also%20found%20its%20way%20into%20pop%20culture.%20Hollywood%20rebels%20Marlon%20Brando%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wild%20One%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1953)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fwhy-the-world-still-remembers-james-dean%2Fa-55093406%5C%22%3EJames%20Dean%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Cem%3ERebel%20Without%20a%20Cause%3C%2Fem%3E%20(1955)%20sported%20an%20iconic%20style%2C%20casually%20wearing%20their%20jackets%20half-zipped%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%201971%2C%20the%20zipper%20still%20managed%20to%20spark%20controversy.%20That%20year%2C%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fmick-jagger-turns-80-the-evolution-of-a-rolling-stones-icon%2Fa-66326219%5C%22%3EThe%20Rolling%20Stones%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ereleased%20their%20legendary%20album%20%E2%80%9CSticky%20Fingers%2C%E2%80%9D%20whose%20album%20cover%20was%20designed%20by%20pop%20art%20icon%20Andy%20Warhol.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20featured%20an%20actual%20metal%20zipper.%20Although%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20reveal%20any%20genitalia%20when%20unzipped%2C%20just%20relatively%20harmless%20cotton%20briefs%2C%20it%20was%20seen%20as%20scandalous%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Spain%2C%20Franco%E2%80%99s%20regime%20censored%20the%20%E2%80%9Cobscene%E2%80%9D%20album%2C%20which%20led%20to%20an%20alternate%20version%20being%20designed%2C%20depicting%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20fingers%20crawling%20out%20of%20a%20tin%20can%20of%20syrup%20%E2%80%93%20which%20many%20find%20far%20more%20disturbing%20than%20zip-up%20pants.%20The%20track%20%E2%80%98Sister%20Morphine%E2%80%99%20also%20had%20to%20be%20removed%20from%20%3Cem%3ESticky%20Fingers%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20the%20Spanish%20market%2C%20even%20though%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20album%E2%80%99s%20tracks%20also%20revolved%20around%20drugs%2C%20from%20%E2%80%98Brown%20Sugar%E2%80%99%20to%20%E2%80%98Bitch.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20130%20years%20after%20it%20was%20first%20patented%2C%20the%20zipper%20is%20here%20to%20stay.%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20YKK%20group%2C%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20zipper%20manufacturer%2C%20produces%20an%20estimated%201.5%20billion%20units%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20simply%20part%20of%20our%20daily%20lives%2C%20mainly%20going%20unnoticed%20%E2%80%93%20until%20it%20gets%20stuck%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20originally%20appeared%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fzip-it-up-the-zippers-130-year-history%2Fa-66660527%5C%22%3EDW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693551880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F01123333%2F4130527119_72f476fff2_c.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fzipper-zip-history-moon-rolling-stones%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20though%20it's%20a%20simple%20everyday%20device%2C%20the%20zipper%20contributed%20to%20the%20iconic%20style%20of%20Hollywood%20rebels%20Marlon%20Brando%20and%20James%20Dean%2C%20flew%20to%20the%20moon%20and%20led%20to%20the%20censorship%20of%20an%20album%20by%20The%20Rolling%20Stones.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fzipper-zip-history-moon-rolling-stones%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Both%20Union%20and%20State%20Govts%20Are%20Confused%20About%20Whom%20to%20Talk%20to%2C'%20Manipur%20CM%20Says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20Manipur%20continues%20to%20reel%20under%20violence%2C%20chief%20minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20on%20Thursday%2C%20August%2031%2C%20said%20that%20there%20are%20too%20many%20civil%20society%20organisations%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20he%20said%20speak%20in%20different%20voices%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20solution%20for%20the%20ethnic%20conflict%20rocking%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20too%20many%20organisations.%20We%20are%20at%20a%20very%20crucial%20stage%20now.%20Both%20the%20central%20and%20the%20state%20governments%20are%20confused%20about%20whom%20to%20talk%20to.%20We%20will%20go%20with%20the%20public%20(opinion)%20and%20never%20work%20against%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fnorth-east%2Ftoo-many-civil-bodies-in-manipur-they-need-to-talk-in-single-voice-cm-biren-singh%2Fcid%2F1962889%5C%22%3Equoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20Singh%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20appealed%20to%20civic%20bodies%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20concrete%20proposal%20and%20to%20speak%20in%20one%20voice%20so%20that%20it%20could%20be%20conveyed%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20violence%20continuing%20unabated%20for%20months%20now%2C%20even%20civil%20society%20organisations%20are%20divided%20on%20community%20lines.%20Both%20Meiteis%20and%20Kukis%2C%20the%20warring%20factions%2C%20have%20community%20organisations%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kukis%20are%20represented%20by%20organisations%20such%20as%20the%20Indigenous%20Tribal%20Leaders%20Forum%20(ITLF)%2C%20Committee%20On%20Tribal%20Unity%20(COTU)%2C%20Kuki%20Inpi%20and%20the%20Zomi%20Council%2C%20Meiteis%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20have%20their%20own%20bodies%20such%20as%20the%20Coordinating%20Committee%20on%20Manipur%20Integrity%20(COCOMI)%2C%20United%20Committee%20Manipur%20(UCM)%2C%20and%20the%20All%20Manipur%20United%20Clubs%20Organisation%20(AMUCO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20made%20his%20comments%20at%20the%20state-level%20celebration%20of%20the%20%E2%80%98Meri%20Maati%20Mera%20Desh%E2%80%99%20programme%20on%20Thursday.%20It%20aims%20for%20a%20unified%20celebration%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20soil%20and%20valour%2C%20commemorating%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20journey%20of%20freedom%20and%20progress.%20This%20campaign%20comprises%20many%20activities%20and%20ceremonies%20conducted%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPeople%20and%20civil%20society%20organisations%20should%20come%20together%20and%20take%20a%20concrete%20proposal%20showing%20their%20stand%20so%20that%20the%20government%20can%20convey%20it%20to%20the%20Centre.%20We%20must%20come%20together%20irrespective%20of%20our%20political%20and%20community%20affiliation%20and%20work%20together%20for%20the%20present%20and%20future%20generation%20to%20enable%20them%20to%20live%20with%20dignity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said%20at%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20condemned%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-two-more-killed-firing-churachandpur-bishnupur-border%5C%22%3Egun%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20August%2029%2C%20on%20farmers%20tending%20their%20fields%20at%20Naransena%20in%20Bishnupur%20district.%20%E2%80%9CSecurity%20forces%20arrested%20one%20person%20in%20this%20connection%20along%20with%20a%20.303%20rifle%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Singh%20may%20have%20been%20appealing%20for%20peace%2C%20there%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmanipur-tribal-mlas-refute-biren-singhs-claim-say-not-in-touch-with-cm%5C%22%3Eallegations%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20him%20that%20he%20has%20been%20favouring%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%2C%20given%20that%20he%20is%20a%20Meitei%20himself.%20Legislators%20from%20his%20own%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20belonging%20to%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20community%20have%20urged%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20remove%20him%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20May%203%2C%20when%20the%20violence%20first%20broke%20out%2C%20more%20than%20160%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%20and%20several%20thousands%20have%20been%20displaced%20from%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693551612000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30163218%2FFwqAt6VXsAIGp1_.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-civil-society-must-speak-in-one-voice-to-end-violence-says-cm-biren-singh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20said%20there%20are%20too%20many%20civic%20bodies%20in%20the%20state%2C%20which%20he%20said%20speak%20in%20different%20voices%2C%20making%20it%20difficult%20to%20arrive%20at%20a%20solution%20for%20the%20ethnic%20conflict.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-civil-society-must-speak-in-one-voice-to-end-violence-says-cm-biren-singh%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Aspirin%20'could%20help%20cut%20diabetes%20risk%20in%20over-65s'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1693549740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F09%2F768x432%2Fskynews-aspirin-bayer-tablet_6269943.jpg%3F20230901074654%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Faspirin-could-help-cut-diabetes-risk-in-over-65s-study-suggests-12951998%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Taking%20aspirin%20every%20day%20could%20lower%20the%20type%202%20diabetes%20risk%20among%20people%20over%2065%2C%20a%20study%20suggests.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A83%2C%22cano